com.interpss.se.record

Interface SEMeasRecord

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SEBaseRecord
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SEMeasRecordImpl

    public interface SEMeasRecord
extends SEBaseRecord
    A representation of the model object 'SE Base Record'. SE base data record class.

    The following features are supported:

    • Status
    • Quality
    • Not Used In Cal
    • Device Id
    • Measure Type
    See Also:
    SERecordPackage.getSEMeasRecord()
